extends includes/header

block content
  include includes/nav
  #header-img
    #image-top
      img(src="static/img/tech-back.jpg" alt="PS4 Controller and Keyboard")
      #top-text
        h1 Miss_Pylons
        h1 Programmer | Gamer
  #about-section
    h2.title-border ABOUT
    .container
      .row.align-items-center.justify-content-center
        .col-lg.align-self-center
          img.img-border(src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/939287918379593728/h8ksMeGU_400x400.jpg" alt="Miss_Pylons")
        .col-lg.align-self-center
          p I found Twitch in 2016 while looking for something to listen to while working on long projects. Though I was a lurker at first, I found a few welcoming communities that pulled me out of the background and into chat. I was impressed with the caring and kind strangers I found in these channels; something you wouldn't think to find on the internet, especially when you can hide behind a username.
          p After a year of watching others stream, I decided to test it out myself. I started with a variety of topics including gaming, cooking, and programming. In November of 2018, I became a Twitch Affiliate. With a goal now to become a Twitch Partner, I am striving to become a better streamer and create a welcoming community for new programmers and avid gamers like myself.
  #schedule-section
    h2.title-border SCHEDULE
    .container
      .row.align-items-center.justify-content-center
